<sect1 id="dir_1f05af774b1537994876600c714c9eab_1autotoc_md235">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::pooling</title><para>GameObject pooling and request handling for efficient object recycling.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1f05af774b1537994876600c714c9eab_1autotoc_md236">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides infrastructure for memory-efficient entity management through object pooling. Pools pre-allocate GameObjects that can be acquired and released during gameplay, avoiding repeated allocation overhead.</para>
</sect1>
